Integrating Meta-Analysis, National Registry, and PHAST and TEDY Trial Data.

Tomee SM(1), Bulder RMA(1), Meijer CA(2), van Berkum I(1), Hinnen JW(3), 
Schoones JW(4), Golledge J(5), Bastiaannet E(6), Matsumura JS(7), Hamming JF(1), 
