HTAD patient pathway: Strategy for diagnostic work-up of patients and families 
with (suspected) heritable thoracic aortic diseases (HTAD). A statement from the 
HTAD working group of VASCERN.

Caruana M(1), Baars MJ(2), Bashiardes E(3), Benke K(4), Björck E(5), Codreanu 
