Employment of cold atmospheric plasma in chilled chicken breasts and the 
analysis of microbial diversity after the shelf-life storage.

Zhao Y(1), Meng Z(1), Shao L(1), Dai R(1), Li X(2), Jia F(3).

Author information:
(1)College of Food Science and Nutritional Engineering, China Agricultural 
University, Beijing 100083, China.
(2)College of Food Science and Nutritional Engineering, China Agricultural 
University, Beijing 100083, China. Electronic address: lixingmin@cau.edu.cn.
(3)Department of Biological and Agricultural Engineering, University of 
