Chromosomal-level genome assembly of potato tuberworm, Phthorimaea operculella: 
a pest of solanaceous crops.

Zhang M(#)(1), Cheng X(#)(2), Lin R(#)(3)(4), Xie B(3), Nauen R(5), Rondon 
